 BBNaija star Erica has asked man identified as Mohammed Jamal better known as White Nigeria where he passed after claiming there’s no pothole from Lagos airport to VI. White Nigerian (Mohammed Jamal) in a tweet said he’s impressed with what the government is doing as he rode from Lagos airport to VI and there was no single pothole. Erica who seems surprised with that asked White Nigerian (Mohammed Jamal) where he passed that there wasn’t any single pothole for her to use that same route next time. Some netizens reacting to that were also curious to know where White Nigerian (Mohammed Jamal) passed so they can also use the route where there’s no single pothole from the airport. 